      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't find another one like this. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept in a climate-controlled garage and pampered every single day. It looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the lot\u2014not a single scratch or smudge to be found! I'm sad to see it go, but I'd love for it to find a home with someone who will appreciate how pristine it is. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
