    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2006 BMW M3 is a superlative example of the E46 platform, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a factory 8,000 RPM redline. Mechanically pristine, this chassis has had the critical rear subframe reinforcement completed, along with a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and preventative rod bearing replacement using VAC coated bearings. The Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission offers crisp, short-throw engagement, directing power through a variable M differential lock. The suspension maintains its original tactile precision, with all bushings and dampers in peak operating condition. Free from common interior delamination or exterior marring, this vehicle delivers an uncompromised, analog driving experience for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
