      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence. This vehicle is in pristine, showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior finish is flawless, featuring a deep, mirror-like luster enhanced by a professional-grade ceramic coating; there are zero stone chips, swirls, or imperfections to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in an 'as-new' state, with the premium leather upholstery still retaining its factory scent and showing absolutely no signs of wear\u2014the bolsters are firm and the carpets have been protected by custom all-weather mats since purchase. Every electronic feature, from the high-fidelity surround sound system to the advanced driver-assist suite, functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a full service history documented exclusively at the original dealership. It rides on original alloy wheels that are entirely free of curb rash, wrapped in high-performance tires with nearly full tread depth. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire a turn-key vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. All manuals, two sets of keys, and a clean title are ready for the next owner.",
